{"tid":115216,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵尖沙咀站列車起火　2男乘客變火人","createTime":"2017-02-10T11:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T11:49:59.000Z","uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93771ab154b73950c28aa6fc80d038e74153fa6f","tid":115216,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:41:28.000Z","msg":"港鐵車廂冒煙4人傷！晚上7時許，港鐵尖沙咀站一列列車的車廂內冒出大量濃煙，尖沙咀站內乘客需疏散。另有消息稱，金鐘站月台現逼滿乘客。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者表示，當時列車離開金鐘前往尖沙咀站，突然列車頭卡接近門口位置起火冒煙，濃煙充斥整個車廂。由於當時正值下班繁忙時間，當時車廂內迫滿乘客，有乘客掩鼻，亦有乘客被火勢波及。當列車進入尖沙咀站月台後，其中一名下半身着火的男乘客衝出月台，需由其他乘客用水協助撲熄火勢。另有一名男子被燒至手腳甩皮，倒臥月台。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人表示，因尖沙咀站發生事故，荃灣線列車將不停尖沙咀站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170210/bkn-20170210192003149-0210_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170210%2Fbkn-20170210192003149-0210_00822_001.html&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=b895742c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170210/bkn-20170210192003149-0210_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2b2ed03e31ca787f2aaf1fb413522cce52f0fa7e","tid":115216,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec914e32a0e05fd687485047df3d9133810dd1d0","tid":115216,"uid":42269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:44:25.000Z","msg":"手機著火？無啦啦下身著火咁搞笑"},{"pid":"936a232917249802686fe785ecd8cdbf690b6f2d","tid":115216,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"冇得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ff9f87e2826bfd0d61b9a155c5e8eedb634c66","tid":115216,"uid":1139,"like":0,"disli